@startuml
title MediMatch – Admin Sequence Diagram
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #1E4B8E
  LifeLineBorderColor #1E4B8E
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #F8FBFF
  ParticipantBorderColor #1E4B8E
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}

actor "Administrator" as Admin
participant "Frontend (UI)" as UI
participant "Backend Server" as Server
database "Database" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

== Login ==
Admin -> UI : Enter Credentials
UI -> Server : Authenticate(Admin Credentials)
Server -> DB : Validate Admin Account
DB --> Server : Auth Successful
Server --> UI : Admin Dashboard Loaded

== Manage Data ==
Admin -> UI : Request Facility Report
UI -> Server : Fetch Facility Data
Server -> DB : Retrieve Listings & Requests
DB --> Server : Data Set
Server -> UI : Display Analytics & Graphs

== Reporting ==
Admin -> Server : Generate Summary Report
Server -> DB : Save Report Entry
Server -> Notify : Send Report Ready Notification
Notify -> Admin : "Report Generated Successfully"

@enduml
